{"tid":389458,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"荷西安歷基宣佈掛靴","createTime":"2017-09-06T09:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T15:09:10.000Z","uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f429fc037b07c90eeb7d7a72aabb4bfe6ce8088","tid":389458,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:32:46.000Z","msg":"Former Liverpool and Newcastle defender Jose Enrique has announced his retirement from football at the age of 31.<br />\n<br />\nThe full-back left Real Zaragoza at the end of last season and told Spanish newspaper Marca that he will stop playing due to a long-term knee injury.<br />\n<br />\nHe said: &quot;I could not play without medication, I did not even train. It was hard, desperate.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Sometimes I got dizzy in training on so much medication.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;After every game my knee swelled like a ball and I was barely able to walk for three days. Something that was supposed to be for three months ended up turning into two years.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I saw five doctors in England but they did not get the problem.<br />\n<br />\nEnrique made 127 appearances for Newcastle between 2007 and 2011 before a &pound;6.5m move to Liverpool, for whom he played 99 times before leaving in September 2016.<br />\n<br />\nHe had surgery on the injury in Spain but the procedure was not enough to save his career.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I was never the same, it was frustrating,&quot; he said. &quot;I was had been playing for three months with a broken meniscus.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I had to escape to Spain because I could not even walk. I could not compete and I had a terrible time.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I had an anxiety attack and thought, 'what the hell is wrong with me?' I did not understand it.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11669/11022840/jose-enrique-retires-due-to-knee-injury\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.skysports.com%2Ffootball%2Fnews%2F11669%2F11022840%2Fjose-enrique-retires-due-to-knee-injury&d=cjmf4A%2BpYGFx723OlEA3xTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=8ebf3488\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11669/11022840/jose-enrique-retires-due-to-knee-injury</a>"},{"pid":"fdb75b92d3c6b634491e3b11b3d079949582d65b","tid":389458,"uid":11270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:33:45.000Z","msg":"同MICHU同一年掛靴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上季都仲踢到廿幾場波估唔到急流勇退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53ef7bfd638e454e7fd6d8de5edae085759887d","tid":389458,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:34:27.000Z","msg":"傻西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3619338a937f5eea1f0336574e9a935335f6fbd3","tid":389458,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:35:23.000Z","msg":"咁後生"},{"pid":"5eb0fd9ea15495ac503c6dbb0c2f698c1e0c2645","tid":389458,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"傻西<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e522e5f24eb023f0b46473092b6a81f783d60bf2","tid":389458,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:34:41.000Z","msg":"卡數果時勁到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d962c23d11c28a910beb6fde58545103407c1da2","tid":389458,"uid":10971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbc9efb2a75a4d884744e5a1aa2ef3637dc3328","tid":389458,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:38:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>卡數果時勁到仆街<im